  "text": "Patient characteristics are summarized in Table 1 . The median age at presentation of symptoms was 2.0 years; at diagnosis it was 5.1 years, and at baseline (start of enzyme therapy) it was 6.8 years. One patient was assessed at baseline conductive hearing loss (range 7-43 dB right ear; 2-53 dB left ear) [CITATION_1] 3 hyperopia only (patient 11). The other patients had at least a follow-up of two years (three assessments) or longer, range 0-4.8 years.",
